e-weighted average of the premium index over the 8-hour period leading to settlement. The rate is capped at ±0.75% per funding interval and settles at 00:00, 08:00, and 16:00 UTC. Funding payments occur automatically between long and short position holders based on the prevailing rate, with no additional fees beyond the standard 0.01% funding charge when applicable."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
